            <p><strong>Downtown Dubai is Emaar's 163-hectare flagship mixed-use development featuring Burj Khalifa (world's tallest building), Dubai Mall (world's most visited shopping destination), Dubai Fountain, and premium residential towers.</strong> Established 2004-2010 and continuously expanding, Downtown represents Dubai's central business and tourism hub with unmatched global brand recognition and sustained capital appreciation from prestige address positioning.</p>
